{"tid":1485293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[假設]示威者入面有鬼唔肯走","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:29:42.000Z","uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3bad35ae728f7ef664345e4f7f7361c182727cb","tid":1485293,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"示威者入面有黑警大家都知<br />\n如果佢地留低唔走，咁我地就會唔想dump低佢離開<br />\n只為我地想齊上齊落<br />\n然後拉曬之後扮示威者既黑警當然會確認身份放返<br />\n<br />\n我唔係要大家捉鬼，因為捉鬼行為無辦法完<br />\n而家如果有咁既情況:<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擺明俾人圍</span></span><br />\n係咪因為有人唔想走所以你唔走？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個時候應該諗下自己同同伴係咪係時候離開</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7ff3c4f04679c950fbc105e2f2ce4236664c1a7","tid":1485293,"uid":284630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"現場好多係假勇武, 花生友<br />\n真勇武前線知道, 豬嘴濾罐係消耗品, 無乜必要都唔會戴<br />\n依家無防暴, 上豬嘴係浪費<br />\n金鐘果班人只係一班裝備撚, 可能連鐵馬都未推過"},{"pid":"75722d360d30c4176399e1a9560ce27c57f7e1fc","tid":1485293,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df96f35f396b3fdc7e713207229183e8f0bf4df7","tid":1485293,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eb6037aa228c3798b4428b0168625a10a04ff3","tid":1485293,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35d73c9e307a7fce24953a813b090a688af6732","tid":1485293,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"有圖有相嘞。唔使假設嘞。"},{"pid":"b649885288bd0a6120def4b1197c46230441aa53","tid":1485293,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08